column16: Elliot Johnson lines out to right fielder Hector Gimenez.
Stephen Vogt grounds out, shortstop Ray Olmedo to first baseman Dan Johnson.
Yuniesky Betancourt pops out to shortstop Alexei Ramirez on the infield fly rule.
Jarrod Dyson walks.    Alex Gordon to 3rd.    Eric Hosmer to 2nd.
Jhan Marinez intentionally walks Eric Hosmer.
Alcides Escobar out on a sacrifice bunt, pitcher Jhan Marinez to second baseman Gordon Beckham.    Alex Gordon to 2nd.
Alex Gordon singles on a soft line drive to left fielder Dayan Viciedo.
Lorenzo Cain lines into double play, second baseman Gordon Beckham to first baseman Paul Konerko.    Jason Bourgeois doubled off 1st.
Salvador Perez singles on a ground ball to left fielder Dayan Viciedo.
Jeff Francoeur grounds out, second baseman Gordon Beckham to first baseman Paul Konerko.
